{"tid":2506140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳肇始今日下午3時會見傳媒 料29號起正式開始落實「疫苗氣泡」","createTime":"2021-04-27T06:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T06:30:02.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2fc9cf840fbd2793d0f8bbdd6093cf03ff2b4fd2","tid":2506140,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:21:52.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局局長陳肇始今日（27日）下午3時在政府總部地下演講廳就最新的社交距離措施會見傳媒。特首林鄭月娥今早預告，記者會將交代最新防疫措施及抗疫新路向，包括擬周四起放寬部分處所復業，落實最新「疫苗氣泡」安排。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局常任秘書長（食物）劉利群、食物環境衞生署署長楊碧筠和食物及衞生局副秘書長（衞生）蔡傑銘，將一同出席記者會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/2057802/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%99%B3%E8%82%87%E5%A7%8B%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%883%E6%99%82%E8%A6%8B%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92-%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%A3%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E8%B7%9D%E9%9B%A2%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F2057802%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%2582%2587%25E5%25A7%258B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25883%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E8%25B7%259D%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%258E%25AA%25E6%2596%25BD&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=ebbc7292\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F2057802%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%2582%2587%25E5%25A7%258B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25883%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E8%25B7%259D%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%258E%25AA%25E6%2596%25BD&h=0d7842bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/2057802/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%99%B3%E8%82%87%E5%A7%8B%